'''气旋艾丽塔'''先后三次[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]非洲东南部岛屿国家[[马达加斯加|马达加斯加]]，属于非常罕见的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]。系统于2004年1月24日在[[莫桑比克海峡|莫桑比克海峡]]发展形成，是[[2003－2004年西南印度洋气旋季|2003－2004年西南印度洋气旋季]]期间第5场获得命名的风暴，增强至[[热带气旋风级|热带气旋强度]]后于1月28日吹袭马达加斯加西北部，在穿越该岛期间减弱成热带低气压，然后进入西南[[印度洋|印度洋]]并转向西进，于1月31日从马达加斯加东部登岸。再度穿过该岛后，气旋回到莫桑比克海峡并再度强化，然后转向东南，于2月3日沿马达加斯加西南部登陆。两天后，艾丽塔开始转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，系统残留的动向仍然飘忽不定，最终于2月13日逐渐消散。

风暴产生的降雨量超过200毫米，马达加斯加有成千上万的房屋受损或被毁。该国5万多人无家可归，其中大部分生活在[[马哈赞加省|马哈赞加省]]和[[图利亚拉省|图利亚拉省]]。气旋引发的洪灾导致超过450平方公里的农地被毁，其中还有重要的粮食作物。艾丽塔夺走岛上33人的生命，这里的灾情还在约两个月后因[[气旋加菲洛|气旋加菲洛]]袭击而进一步加剧。风暴还给[[莫桑比克|莫桑比克]]和[[马拉维|马拉维]]带去降水并造成破坏，系统的外围风场也在[[塞舌尔|塞舌尔]]、[[毛里求斯|毛里求斯]]和[[留尼汪|留尼汪]]产生阵风和强烈的海浪。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Elita 2004 track.png}}
2004年1月25日，[[马达加斯加|马达加斯加]]以西约95公里的[[莫桑比克海峡|莫桑比克海峡]]内发展出[[雷暴|雷暴]]区<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Mohammed, Dixon, Jacobs, & Schultz | year = 2004 | title = January 25 Significant Tropical Weather Advisory | publisher = Joint Typhoon Warning Center}}</ref>，系统的中到下层[[大气环流|环流]]周围发展出深层[[对流|对流]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Mohammed, Dixon, Jacobs, & Schultz | year = 2004 | title = January 26 Significant Tropical Weather Advisory | publisher = Joint Typhoon Warning Center}}</ref>，[[法国气象局|法国气象局]]于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]1月26日早上6点将位于马达加斯加[[迈因蒂拉努|迈因蒂拉努]]以西约105公里海域的系统归类为第06号热带扰动<ref>{{cite report | author = La Réunion - Météo-France | year = 2004 | title = Tropical Disturbance 06 Advisory 1}}</ref>，再于6小时后将其升级为第06号热带低气压<ref>{{cite report | author = La Réunion - Météo-France | year = 2004 | title = Tropical Depression 06 Advisory 2}}</ref>，26日晚，低气压获名“艾丽塔”（{{lang|en|Elita}}）<ref name="mf3">{{cite report | author = La Réunion - Météo-France | year = 2004 | title = Tropical Depression 06 (Elita) Advisory 3}}</ref>。[[联合台风警报中心|联合台风警报中心]]也在这时开始针对气旋发布公告<ref name="discos">{{cite web | author = Joint Typhoon Warning Center | year = 2004 | title = Advisories for Tropical Cyclone Elita | accessdate = 2015-04-11 | url = http://www.australiasevereweather.com/cyclones/2004/elita.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120207025528/http://www.australiasevereweather.com/cyclones/2004/elita.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-02-07}}</ref>。由于中等强度[[风切变|风切变]]令北部的对流受限，气旋起初的增强速度缓慢<ref name="mf3" />。受西面存在的[[高压脊|高压脊]]影响，风暴形成早期总体向北移动，逐渐逼近[[赤道|赤道]]，对于西南印度洋的热带气旋来说，这种情况很不寻常<ref name="gp">{{cite web | author = Gary Padgett | year = 2004 | title = January 2004 Worldwide Tropical Cyclone Summary | accessdate = 2015-04-11 | url = http://www.australiasevereweather.com/cyclones/2004/summ0401.htm | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150208040004/http://australiasevereweather.com/cyclones/2004/summ0401.htm | archivedate = 2015-02-08}}</ref>。

1月27日清晨，法国气象局将艾丽塔升级成热带风暴<ref>{{cite report | author = La Réunion - Météo-France | year = 2004 | title = Tropical Storm Elita Advisory 4}}</ref>，但系统在当天下午就减弱成了热带低气压<ref>{{cite report | author = La Réunion - Météo-France | year = 2004 | title = Tropical Depression 06 (ex-Elita) Advisory 6}}</ref>。1月28日清晨，气旋又达到热带风暴强度<ref>{{cite report | author = La Réunion - Météo-France | year = 2004 | title = Tropical Storm Elita Advisory 8}}</ref>，对流也有进一步增长<ref>{{cite report | author = La Réunion - Météo-France | year = 2004 | title = Tropical Storm Elita Advisory 9}}</ref>。受北面的高压脊影响，艾丽塔转向[[罗盘方位|东南偏东]]<ref name="gp" />，并在逼近陆地期间迅速强化，卫星图像显示系统中已经逐渐发展出清晰的[[风眼|风眼]]<ref>{{cite web | author = La Réunion - Météo-France | year = 2004 | title = Tropical Storm Elita Advisory 10}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}1月28日中午12点，风暴达到[[热带气旋风级|热带气旋强度]]，相当于飓风强度的最低标准{{#tag:ref|飓风是指风速在每小时119公里或以上的[[太平洋飓风|东太平洋]]和[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]<ref name="glos">{{cite report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-03-25 | accessdate = 2014-06-15 | title = Glossary of NHC Terms | archivedate = 2014-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140601020814/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml}}</ref>。|group="注"}}<ref name="tcr">{{cite web | author = La Réunion - Météo-France | year = 2004 | title = Forte Tempete tropicale: Elita | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006083554/http://www.meteo.fr/temps/domtom/La_Reunion/TGPR/saison20032004B/05.html | accessdate = 2015-04-11 | url = http://www.meteo.fr/temps/domtom/La_Reunion/TGPR/saison20032004B/05.html | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2014-10-06 }}</ref>。三小时后，艾丽塔以阵风时速超过180公里强度从布贝托克湾（{{lang|en|Bombetoka Bay}}）[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]马达加斯加西北部<ref name="wmo">{{cite web | author = RA I Tropical Cyclone Committee for the Southwest Indian Ocean | year = 2005 | title = Seventeenth Session for the Tropical Cyclone Committee | publisher = World Meteorological Organization | accessdate = 2015-04-11 | archivedate = 2012-07-17 | url = http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/documents/RAITCC-17En.pdf | format = PDF | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120717054942/http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/documents/RAITCC-17En.pdf}}</ref>。气旋在陆地上空迅速减弱成热带低气压<ref>{{cite report | author = La Réunion - Météo-France | year = 2004 | title = Tropical Depression Elita Advisory 12}}</ref>，但在穿过该岛后又在马达加斯加以东海域重新发展。1月30日时，艾丽塔已进入西南印度洋<ref name="gp" />，其对流快速组织成[[雨带|雨带]]<ref>{{cite report | author = La Réunion - Météo-France | year = 2004 | title = Tropical Disturbance 06 (ex-Elita) Advisory 17}}</ref>。系统在马达加斯加近海向南飘移了少许距离，并在此期间逐渐增强，于{{lang|en|UTC}}1月31日凌晨0点再次达到热带风暴强度标准<ref name="gp" />。根据法国气象局的记录，艾丽塔转向西进，在约6小时后以风力时速75公里强度从[[马南扎里|马南扎里]]附近登岸<ref name="gp" /><ref>{{cite report | author = La Réunion - Météo-France | year = 2004 | title = Tropical Storm Elita Advisory 20}}</ref>。

风暴在向西穿越马达加斯加期间迅速减弱为热带低气压，于1月31日晚回到莫桑比克海峡。到达开放水域上空后，系统中的深层对流再次增加，[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]也逐渐改善。受北面逐渐增强的高压脊影响，艾丽塔的前进速度放缓，然后转向东南偏东。2月2日晚，联合台风警报中心估计气旋达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时120公里的最高强度，法国气象局也在不久后宣布风暴达到风力时速110公里的最高强度。2月3日清晨，艾丽塔以最高强度从[[穆龙达瓦|穆龙达瓦]]附近上岸，然后在第三次穿越该岛期间快速弱化，于{{lang|en|UTC}}2月4日凌晨0点以热带低气压强度再次进入西南印度洋。气象机构一度预测低气压会再度强化，但艾丽塔实际上加速向东南方向移动，并在此期间逐渐失去残余的对流，风暴中心也在强烈上层[[低压槽|低压槽]]的影响下暴露出来。到2月5日时，系统已转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，并因受弱转向气流影响而暂时停止移动。<ref name="gp" />接下来的一星期里，艾丽塔的残留在马达加斯加东南方向洋面蜿蜒行进，最终于2月13日逐渐消散<ref name="tcr" />。

气旋艾丽塔先后三次穿越马达加斯加，这样的情况非常罕见，但并非史无前例。1970年1月的[[1969－1970年西南印度洋气旋季|强烈热带风暴费利西亚]]和1982年的风暴贾斯汀都曾达成过这一目标。<ref name="wmo" />

== 影响 ==
[[Image:Elita_(2004)_rain_density.jpg|200px]]

[[莫桑比克国家气象局|莫桑比克国家气象局]]建议生活在[[楠普拉省|楠普拉省]]、[[赞比西亚省|赞比西亚省]]、[[索法拉省|索法拉省]]和[[伊尼扬巴内省|伊尼扬巴内省]]的居民做好应对狂风暴雨的准备<ref name="Xinhua TS affects Mozambique">{{cite news | archivedate = 2015-04-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150411164933/http://reliefweb.int/report/mozambique/tropical-storm-affects-mozambique | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mozambique/tropical-storm-affects-mozambique | title = Tropical storm affects Mozambique | publisher = Xinhua News Agency | date = 2004-02-03 | accessdate = 2015-04-12 }}</ref>。楠普拉省有超过2000幢建筑被毁，受灾最严重的是房屋总体建筑质量较差的门巴（{{lang|en|Memba}}）、纳卡拉-贝拉（{{lang|en|Nacala-a-Velha}}）、莫任夸尔（{{lang|en|Mogincual}}）和[[楠普拉|楠普拉市]]。其中楠普拉市有一间学校受到严重破坏，纳卡拉-贝拉的幸存者在1月29日晚不得不露宿街头<ref name="Xinhua Nampula Mozambique">{{cite news | title = Storm hits Nampula province of Mozambique | publisher = Xinhua News Agency | accessdate = 2015-04-12 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mozambique/storm-hits-nampula-province-mozambique | date = 2004-01-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150411170147/http://reliefweb.int/report/mozambique/storm-hits-nampula-province-mozambique | archivedate = 2015-04-11 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。艾丽塔一共对莫桑比克的[[莫桑比克行政区划|四个省]]构成影响，其中大部分发生在[[伊尼扬巴内|伊尼扬巴内]]到楠普拉市之间的沿海地区<ref name="Xinhua TS affects Mozambique" />。风暴气流将[[热带辐合带|热带辐合带]]的湿气带到[[马拉维|马拉维]]，产生的降雨量超过150毫米，倾盆大雨摧毁了[[卡龙加|卡龙加区]]的80余套房屋和一间诊所。此外，[[塞舌尔|塞舌尔]]也受到风暴产生的巨浪、阵风和降水影响。<ref name="wmo" />

首度登陆马达加斯加期间，气旋沿途普降暴雨，最高降雨量达715毫米<ref>{{cite web | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 2004 | accessdate = 2015-04-12 | title = Cyclone Elita (09S) Cumulative Track and rainfall | url = http://www.cpc.ncep.noaa.gov/products/fews/CYCLONES/elita_track.pdf | format = PDF | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120315155610/http://www.cpc.ncep.noaa.gov/products/fews/CYCLONES/elita_track.pdf | archivedate = 2012-03-15}}</ref>，[[安楚希希|安楚希希]]的24小时降雨量高达222毫米。[[马哈赞加|马哈赞加]]的阵风时速超过180公里<ref name="wmo" />。艾丽塔首次登陆就令沿途约5000人流离失所，[[马哈赞加省|马哈赞加省]]西北部有90%的建筑物因风暴受损，至少两人遇难<ref name="jtwc">{{cite web | author = Joint Typhoon Warning Center | year = 2005 | title = Report on Tropical Cyclone Elita (09S) | accessdate = 2015-04-12 | archivedate = 2013-12-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131206154117/http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/atcr/2004atcr.pdf | url = http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/atcr/2004atcr.pdf}}</ref>。马达加斯加共有1万2408套房屋被毁或严重受损<ref name="ifrc33">{{cite web | author = International Federation of Red Cross And Red Crescent Societies | date = 2004-03-03 | title = Madagascar: Cyclone Elita Information Bulletin No. 1 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2015-04-12 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/madagascar/madagascar-cyclone-elita-information-bulletin-no-1 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150412043116/http://reliefweb.int/report/madagascar/madagascar-cyclone-elita-information-bulletin-no-1 | archivedate = 2015-04-12}}</ref>，导致5万5983人无家可归<ref name="wmo" />，其中大部分生活在马哈赞加省和[[图利亚拉省|图利亚拉省]]<ref name="act227" />。该国有约7000人被迫前往体育场馆或依然屹立的建筑物中寻求庇护。此外，马达加斯加共有510所学校和医院受到严重破坏。气旋对马达加斯加[[马达加斯加行政区划|全部6个省中的5个]]构成影响，部分地区的道路供电都受到严重扰乱<ref name="ifrc33" />，至少39座桥梁受损或被毁<ref name="act227">{{cite web | author = Action by Churches Together International | date = 2004-02-27 | title = ACT Appeal Madagascar: Cyclone Relief AFMG-41 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/madagascar/act-appeal-madagascar-cyclone-relief-afmg-41 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150412044247/http://reliefweb.int/report/madagascar/act-appeal-madagascar-cyclone-relief-afmg-41 | accessdate = 2015-04-12 | archivedate = 2015-04-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[邁因蒂拉努|邁因蒂拉努]]和苏阿维南德里亚纳（{{lang|en|Soavinandriana}}）都受到风暴重创<ref name="wmo" />。暴雨引发的洪水淹没了[[米东吉-阿齐莫|米东吉-阿齐莫]]（{{lang|en|Midongy Atismo}}）80%的[[水稻|水稻]]<ref>{{cite web | author = Integrated Regional Information Networks | date = 2004-02-16 | title = Aid urgent after Elita sows destruction | publisher = United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/madagascar/madagascar-aid-urgent-after-elita-sows-destruction | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-04-12 | archivedate = 2015-04-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150412044924/http://reliefweb.int/report/madagascar/madagascar-aid-urgent-after-elita-sows-destruction}}</ref>，[[玉米|玉米]]和[[木薯|木薯]]作物都受到类似影响。受害作物都是马达加斯加人的口粮<ref name="ifrc33" />，风暴还破坏了该国超过450平方公里的农地<ref name="usaid" />。整个马达加斯加共有至少33人丧生，另有至少129人受伤<ref name="wmo" />。

艾丽卡的温带天气系统残留产生狂风和巨浪，对[[毛里求斯|毛里求斯]]和[[留尼汪|留尼汪]]构成冲击，导致一艘船沉没<ref name="gp" />。

== 余波 ==
[[Image:Cyclone_Elita_Run-off.jpg|right]]

2004年2月13日，马达加斯加政府向[[国际社会|国际社会]]请求援助<ref name="afp213" />。风暴过去1个月时，[[法国政府|法国]]、[[美国联邦政府|美国]]、[[德国政治|德国]]和[[日本政府|日本]]一共提供了价值28万7000美元（2004年[[美元|美元]]）的援助<ref name="usaid">{{cite web | author = Tamra Halmrast-Sanchez | year = 2004 | title = Southern Africa Information Bulletin #2 | publisher = United States Agency for International Development | accessdate = 2008-01-20 | format = PDF | url = http://www.usaid.gov/our_work/humanitarian_assistance/disaster_assistance/countries/southern_africa/fy2004/SouthernAfrica_UP_IB02-05-21-2004.pdf | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-02-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120217183521/http://www.usaid.gov/our_work/humanitarian_assistance/disaster_assistance/countries/southern_africa/fy2004/SouthernAfrica_UP_IB02-05-21-2004.pdf}}</ref><ref name="afp213" /><ref name="ga" /><ref name="ja" />。法国政府派出载有食品、医药及其它物资的飞机赶赴灾区<ref name="afp213">{{cite web | author = Agence France-Presse | date = 2004-02-13 | title = Madagascar seeks aid after storm kills 29, leaves 44,000 homeless | accessdate = 2015-04-12 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/madagascar/madagascar-seeks-aid-after-storm-kills-29-leaves-44000-homeless | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150412051454/http://reliefweb.int/report/madagascar/madagascar-seeks-aid-after-storm-kills-29-leaves-44000-homeless | archivedate = 2015-04-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，德国政府提供的主要是食品和药品援助<ref name="ga">{{cite web | author = Government of Germany | year = 2004 | title = Federal Foreign Office makes available 70,000 euro for victims of the tropical cyclone "Elita" in Madagascar | accessdate = 2015-04-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150412051646/http://reliefweb.int/report/madagascar/federal-foreign-office-makes-available-70000-euro-victims-tropical-cyclone-elita | archivedate = 2015-04-12 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/madagascar/federal-foreign-office-makes-available-70000-euro-victims-tropical-cyclone-elita}}</ref>。2月27日，日本政府向马加达加斯送去包括帐篷、发电机和塑料板材在内的多种救灾物资<ref name="ja">{{cite web | author = Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Japan | date = 2004-02-27 | title = Emergency Assistance to Madagascar for Cyclone Disaster | accessdate = 2015-04-12 | url = http://www.mofa.go.jp/announce/announce/2004/2/0227-2.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006070912/http://www.mofa.go.jp/announce/announce/2004/2/0227-2.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-07-14}}</ref>。

官员向灾区发放包括大米、糖、肥皂、蜡烛、火柴和净水药片在内的多种救灾物资。政府在图利亚拉省的穆龙达瓦发放了4万吨水稻种子，[[塔那那利佛省|塔那那利佛省]]的安巴图兰皮派发了10吨大米，此外，[[世界粮食计划署|世界粮食计划署]]还向该国送去80吨面粉。[[联合国|联合国]]与多家援助机构通力合作，修复了多所学校，并向灾区居民提供膳食。工人协会与马加达斯加[[国际红十字与红新月运动|红十字会]]合作设立供水系统，每天可以提供4万5000升饮用水。<ref name="ifrc33" />

气旋艾丽塔来袭约两个月后，马达加斯加又遭[[气旋加菲洛|气旋加菲洛]]袭击，破坏程度严重加剧，造成数百人死亡，超过24万人无家可归<ref name="wmo" />。

